Package: TensorMCMC
Type: Package
Title: Tensor Regression with Stochastic Low-Rank Updates
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-12-07
Authors@R: person("Ritwick", "Mondal", email = "ritwick12@tamu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ritwick Mondal <ritwick12@tamu.edu>
Description: Implements low-rank tensor regression for tensor predictors and scalar covariates
            using random-walk stochastic updates. Includes C++ acceleration for coefficient
            updates and prediction, as well as utilities for cross-validation and error metrics.
